divs: Sighting DetailsI was standing outside of my back door and thought I was taking a picture of a jet that didn't look to be moving. It was about a year later when I was going over my photos and I zoomed in on what I was taking a picture of. It is obviously not a jet or weather balloon. The last photo looks like there is a plume like they both took off at a very high speed. If you can tell me what you think this is, I would very much appriciate it.
